  "title": "Architectural Assistant",
  "description": "<p>About The Role</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>You will be working on various local projects to collaborate in a teamwork environment to design, document and deliver excellent architecture. You will interface with external clients, consultants and stakeholders to complete project tasks independently or with the team.</li>\n  <li>Involvement in concept design, design development, preparation of drawings and models</li>\n  <li>Assist in project execution and administration throughout the project cycle</li>\n  <li>Work with clients, consultants and other stakeholders</li>\n  <li>Assist to ensure that the building plans meet the necessary building codes and regulations</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>• Diploma/ Bachelor’s Degree in Architecture or related fields</p>\n<p>• Minimum 3 years of relevant architectural experience preferred</p>\n<p>• Experience in Public Housing projects preferred</p>\n<p>• Good knowledge of architectural details, working drawings and construction practices</p>\n<p>• Conversant with local codes &amp; regulations</p>\n<p>• Knowledge of Autocad, Revit</p>\n<p>• Good communication skills and positive attitude</p>",
